milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (313) involving teams Kenya & Scotland in ODIs
John Blain has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (18) for SCOT, going past Hamilton

stories.title: Obuya powers Kenya to title glory
stories.subTitle: Kenya v Scotland, WCL final, Nairobi
stories.summary: It ought to have been the series showcase but Scotland's batting crashed in the final of the World Cricket League at the Gymkhana Ground in Nairobi before a fierce innings from David Obuya carried Kenya to the title on home soil
